'From Squeak3.1alpha [latest update: #''Squeak3.1alpha'' of 12 February 2001 update 3910] on 18 April 2001 at 5:33:55 pm'!"Change Set:		haloContrast-bfDate:			18 April 2001Author:			Bert FreudenbergMakes halo icons more contrasting with the background. Postscriptum changes recolor icon to 1 bit depth."!!Color methodsFor: 'conversions' stamp: 'bf 4/18/2001 16:25'!makeForegroundColor        "Make a foreground color contrasting with me"        ^self luminance >= 0.5                ifTrue: [Color black]                ifFalse: [Color white]! !"Postscript:Change recolor halo icon to 1 bit depth"ScriptingSystem saveForm: ((ScriptingSystem formAtKey: 'Halo-Recolor') asFormOfDepth: 1) atKey: 'Halo-Recolor'!